The paper deals with a communication problem involving limited energy and delay constraints, which is a common topic in information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI). The optimization problem is convex, which is a common theme in control and optimization (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions a discretized version of the problem, which involves partitioning, a topic commonly studied in algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and multimedia (cs.MM).
